{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "叶慕华及时赶到救下宇文雄，与风从龙展开激战。叶慕华以大乘般若掌克制风从龙的大擒拿手，最终在宇文雄配合下擒获风从龙。叶慕华以独门手法折磨风从龙逼供，风从龙招供叶屠户父子的阴谋：叶凌风是朝廷奸细，叶屠户故意诈败以骗取义军信任，计划在义军总攻小金川时设下埋伏将其一网打尽。叶慕华还查出三年前麦积石山围攻案的真相——消息是耿总兵营中暗探偷听泄露的，与耿秀凤无关。审问将毕时，武功极高的欧阳大娘突然出现，以指环暗器解了风从龙穴道并打落宇文雄长剑，风从龙趁机逃脱在即。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知死活的小贼，你赶来送死，我就一并打发你吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "你这大擒拿手法还欠高明！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "我说你还欠高明，说得不错吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "你是什么人？你可知道我又是什么人？我劝你还是不要趁这趟浑水的好。这小子是朝廷叛逆，你知道么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "叶大哥，这个老贼是朝廷鹰爪，别放过他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "风从龙，你不知道我，我可是知道你的。我知道你是陕甘总督的护院，不，现在是四川总督的护院了。你不在四川伺候你的主子，来到这里做什么？快快从实招来，我或者还可饶你一命，否则，哼，哼，我可是专杀狗腿子的！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "风大护院，你碰上了我，可由不得你了。还想跑么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "好小子，你当我怕你不成！我不过爱惜你的武功得来不易罢了。你的师父是什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "待会儿我自然会审问你的，却轮不到你来问我！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "一剑将他杀掉，那是太便宜他了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "不错，咱们找个僻静之处，审问他吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "这厮不是普通的鹰爪，为他而耽搁一些时候，也是值得的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "风大护院，你审犯人也审得多了，今日可轮到你受审啦，识相的就依实供来，若存半句虚言，叫你识得我的厉害！先说，你这次是为了什么进京的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "大大夫死则死耳，你这两个小子也配审问我么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "好，你笑吧！我倒要看你这个'硬汉子'能充得多久？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "你，你干脆一剑杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "杀你？没这么便宜！你不是要充'硬汉子'么？怎么，我只是小施刑罚你就受不起了？我还有十几种更厉害的刑罚准备让你尝尝滋味呢！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "小祖宗，你松松刑吧，我说，我说，我说了！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "你笑不出来了吧？哼，也不怕你不说！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "你这次进京来作什么？快说！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我给叶大人来京禀报军情，并请皇上给他增兵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "什么军情？为何不用文书，要你亲口禀报？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "你是不是想受更厉害的毒刑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "叶大人打了几次败伏，这是故意诈败的。他要我密奏皇上，请皇上安心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "何以他要诈败？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "这个是与他的公子有关吧？老实告诉你，叶廷宗的来历我早已知道。你说假话也瞒不过我的。你说假话，只有你自己吃亏！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是叶廷宗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "叶廷宗就是你的大师兄叶凌风本来的名字，也就是这位风大护院的少主人，四川总督叶屠户的公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我全说了，你松松刑吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "叶屠户父子两人定下了什么阴谋诡计准备对付义军？快快从实招来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "这是军机大事，我、我不过是个护院，怎能知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好狠的手段！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "这计划准备在什么时候进行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我所知道的都已说了，请两位小英雄高抬贵首。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "再问你一桩事情。三年前有十三名大内高手在甘肃的麦积石山围攻一个少年，这个少年就是你们的总督少爷如今冒了他的名字的那个叶凌风。而这十三名大内高手之中，有七个人当时就是住在陕甘总督的衙门的。你身为总督的护院，这件事你应该是知道的了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我知道这件事情，但当时我可没有同去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "我知道你没有同去。但那一班大内高手怎知道那一日叶凌风会到麦积石山的药王庙？这消息是谁密告的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "你们明明知道耿总兵和那姓叶的少年是毫无关系的，为何你的主人，当时的陕甘总督财叶屠户却要借此一案陷害耿总兵？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "原来如此，可惜，可惜……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "可惜什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "没什么，可惜这里只有咱们两人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "好，最后间你一桩事情，叶廷宗充当朝廷的奸细。这是几时开始的？是否由你从中穿针引线？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我所知道的尽都说了，两位小英雄若肯饶我，以后我也不敢再当朝廷的鹰犬啦。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "当真都说了么？宇文兄，搜搜他的身子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "宇文兄，这两份文件对你或许会有用处，你妥为收藏吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "这厮该当如何处置。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "这样的人决计不能相信，饶他少受一点活罪，给他一个痛快吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们怎么说话不算数！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "我几时答应过饶你的命的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我吐露了这许多秘密，即使不能将功赎罪，也总可以稍减几分吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "叶大哥，废他武功如何？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "不能因只顾妇人之仁误了大事！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还有一件机密之事，你们要不要知道？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "有什么机密之事，快说！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "唉，这个，这个……你们可能饶我一条性命？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "你不必说了。我不能饶你性命，不用骗我！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "speaker_name": "风从龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在想要杀我，已经迟了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里来的妖妇，胆敢暗器伤人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳大娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_cong_long",
      "text": "有我在此，谁还能够伤害你？风从龙你不用跑啦！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_da_niang",
      "text": "你是谁，为何助这鹰爪？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳大娘",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "混帐，你骂谁是鹰爪？我的事情你管得着么？我喜欢帮谁就帮谁！你要知道我是什么人，你先绪我磕头！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳大娘",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我骂你的母亲，你就生气了么？哼，欧阳婉这贱婢见了我，她也要向我磕头，让我喜欢怎样骂就怎样骂！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你宝剑虽利、岂能奈我何哉？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "撤手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "text": "字文兄，杀那鹰爪要紧，你让我暂时抵挡一阵。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在我的眼皮底下，你们还想走得出去伤人么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46
    },
